<p>
  <span class="nym">Savage</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Anglo-Norman</span> <i>savage</i>, <span class="lang">Anglo-Norman</span>, <span class="lang">Old French</span> <i>salvage</i> 'savage, wild, in a state of nature', from <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>silvaticus, salvaticus</i> 'woodland, wild'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


